plot: Okabe needs to find a very old computer to hack a very new tech.

With further information about SERN's time travel experiments encrypted in a code that Daru can't decipher, Okabe learns from John Titor that he needs the IBN-5100 computer Moeka was looking for to decode it. Whilst doing his laundry, Okabe runs into Kurisu, who is still in denial about a time machine existing. After Mayuri hears from her maid café co-worker, Rumiho "Feiris Nyan Nyan" Akiha, that she knows about the IBN-5100, Okabe finds out that the computer is at the shrine where Ruka works. Okabe and Kurisu borrow it from Ruka's father and carry it back to the lab.—Wikipedia
